                                "mergeField": "%3Cdiv%3E%3Cspan%20style=%22font-size:%2012pt;%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EGuidance%20for%20Disclosure%20407-1%20%3C/strong%3E%3C/span%3E%3C/div%3E%0A%3Cdiv%3EThe%20process%20for%20identifying%20operations%20and%20suppliers,%20as%20specified%20in%20Disclosure%20407-1,%20can%20reflect%20the%20reporting%20organization&rsquo;s%20approach%20to%20risk%20assessment%20on%20this%20issue.%20It%20can%20also%20draw%20from%20recognized%20international%20data%20sources,%20such%20as%20the%20various%20outcomes%20of%20the%20ILO%20Supervisory%20bodies%20and%20the%20recommendations%20of%20the%20ILO%20Committee%20of%20Freedom%20of%20Association.%3C/div%3E%0A%3Cdiv%3EWhen%20reporting%20the%20measures%20taken,%20the%20organization%20can%20refer%20to%20the%20ILO%20&lsquo;Tripartite%20Declaration%20of%20Principles%20Concerning%20Multinational%20Enterprises%20and%20Social%20Policy&rsquo;%20and%20Organisation%20for%20Economic%20Co-operation%20and%20Development%20(OECD)%20OECD%20Guidelines%20for%20Multinational%20Enterprises%20for%20further%20guidance.%3C/div%3E%0A%3Cdiv%3E&nbsp;%3C/div%3E%0A%3Cdiv%3E%3Cstrong%3EBackground%3C/strong%3E%3C/div%3E%0A%3Cdiv%3EThis%20disclosure%20concerns%20an%20organization&rsquo;s%20due%20diligence%20with%20respect%20to%20any%20negative%20impacts%20its%20activities%20have%20had%20on%20the%20human%20rights%20of%20workers%20to%20form%20or%20join%20trade%20unions%20and%20to%20bargain%20collectively.%20This%20can%20include%20policies%20and%20processes%20with%20respect%20to%20the%20organization's%20business%20relationships,%20including%20its%20suppliers.%20It%20can%20also%20include%20the%20due%20diligence%20process%20to%20identify%20operations%20and%20suppliers%20where%20these%20rights%20are%20at%20risk.%3C/div%3E%0A%3Cdiv%3EIt%20also%20aims%20to%20reveal%20actions%20that%20have%20been%20taken%20to%20support%20these%20rights%20across%20an%20organization&rsquo;s%20range%20of%20operations.%20This%20disclosure%20does%20not%20require